QuestData.Title: The Enemy of Our Enemy
QuestData.Description: You have done us a great service, $c.$b$bWhile they remain an imposing force, your efforts have kept an important artifact from the naga.$b$bI shall write to my peers of your findings. Meanwhile, the water revenant on Ranazjar Isle has stood alone against a steady onslaught of naga.$b$bI would have you find him and determine if there is some way we can assist him.
QuestData.LogDescription: Cenarion Researcher Korrah wants you to speak with Lord Hydronis.
QuestData.RewardText: I have witnessed your actions here, $r.$b$bYour presence here is both welcome and timely.
